Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:26.29,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:924002,926295}Professor, Mine-san's melody is a plagiarism!{NOTE:先生。峰さんのは盗作です！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.50,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:926295,928506}{\i1}No way!{NOTE:そんな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:32.80,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:930174,932802}That's not true. I wrote this melody myself yesterday.{NOTE:違います。この曲は私が昨日…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:34.63,Default,Music teacher,0,0,0,,{TIME:932802,934637}Hold on.{NOTE:待ちたまえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:39.26,Default,Music teacher,0,0,0,,{TIME:934637,939267}You didn't cooperate with this melody, did you?{NOTE:君たちがこのメロディーを合作したんじゃないのかね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:40.47,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:939267,940476}No, we didn't.{NOTE:いいえ、違います。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.47,0:15:43.52,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:940476,943521}I don't need to cooperate with Mine-san.{NOTE:私峰さんなんかと合作する必要ありませんからね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:46.19,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:943521,946190}But I really did write it myself.{NOTE:でも、このメロディー確かに私が。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:50.73,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:946190,950737}Then you ought to be more confident if that indeed is the case.{NOTE:それなら自身を持って、もっと堂々と歌いたいんじゃないかしら。堂々と。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:52.44,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:950737,952447}But that's—{NOTE:でも、すれは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:54.57,Default,Music teacher,0,0,0,,{TIME:952447,954574}Kōda! Mine!{NOTE:香田、峰！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:55.86,Default,Music teacher,0,0,0,,{TIME:954574,955867}Come with me.{NOTE:二人共、来なさい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:06.91,Default,Music teacher,0,0,0,,{TIME:965251,966919}Listen. Be honest with me.{NOTE:いいか？素直に言うんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:09.75,Default,Music teacher,0,0,0,,{TIME:966919,969756}Which one of you has composed this melody?{NOTE:どっちが作ったメロディーなんだね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:11.17,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:969756,971174}I didn't copy anything.{NOTE:盗作じゃありません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:13.71,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:971174,973718}Then you're saying I did?{NOTE:じゃ、私がやったとおっしゃるのね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:16.13,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:973718,976137}No… I don't know.{NOTE:そういう訳じゃ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:18.09,Default,Music teacher,0,0,0,,{TIME:976137,978097}Cut it out already!{NOTE:二人共お止めなさい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:23.35,Default,Music teacher,0,0,0,,{TIME:978097,983352}Have it your way. We'll suspend the contest until one of you starts telling the truth.{NOTE:とにかく、どちらかが正直に言ってくれるまでコンクールへの参加は中止する。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.39,0:16:26.77,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:984395,986773}Do you think I'd do such a thing?{NOTE:私大変迷惑です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:27.85,Default,Music teacher,0,0,0,,{TIME:986773,987857}Kōda-kun!{NOTE:香田くん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:31.06,Default,Music teacher,0,0,0,,{TIME:988566,991069}I don't know anything.{NOTE:少し興奮しすぎとるぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:32.57,Default,Music teacher,0,0,0,,{TIME:991069,992570}Same goes to you, Mine-kun.{NOTE:それに、峰くん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:34.73,Default,Music teacher,0,0,0,,{TIME:992570,994739}I want the culprit to denounce herself.{NOTE:君も素直さが足りにな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:41.03,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:999786,1001037}{\i1}This can't be happening.{NOTE:酷いわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:46.41,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004040,1006417}Do you see now, Professor?{NOTE:これでお分かり、先生？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:48.08,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006417,1008086}She ran away because she's scared.{NOTE:自身がないから逃げらしたんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:59.01,Sign,(sign),0,0,10,,{TIME:1013508,1019013}{\fs28\bord2.5}Spring Intro · Kōda Miki\NSong of Heart · Lyrics and melody by Mine Nozomi{NOTE:春のイントロ・香田美紀\\N心の歌・作詞作曲峰のぞみ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:02.30,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021265,1022308}Ōsaki-san.{NOTE:おおさきさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:05.31,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022308,1025311}Why did you teach our melody to that poor lass?{NOTE:なぜあんな貧乏人の娘にメロディーを教えたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:08.52,Default,Ōsaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025311,1028523}Ah, you see, that's…{NOTE:あ、はい、それは…その…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:12.94,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028523,1032944}Don't tell me you felt pity for a fellow poor girl.{NOTE:まさか貧乏人同士で哀れみあって教えたのではないでしょうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:14.69,Default,Ōsaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032944,1034695}No, not at all.{NOTE:いいえ、とんでもない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.69,0:17:18.40,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034695,1038407}Then why did you teach her, Ōsaki-san?{NOTE:じゃ、どうしてあの人に教えたんです、おおさきさん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:21.41,Default,Ōsaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038407,1041410}I-I didn't know she was your rival…{NOTE:いや、まさかあの娘さんがお嬢様のライバルとはし—}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:24.20,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041410,1044205}You taught her because you didn't know that?{NOTE:知らなかったから教えたって言うの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:26.33,Default,Ōsaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044205,1046332}No, actually…{NOTE:いいえ、私はあの人に…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:28.45,Default,Ōsaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046332,1048459}Rather than teaching her…{NOTE:…教えたんじゃなくて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.45,0:17:29.79,Default,Ōsaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048459,1049794}…I heard it from her.{NOTE:…教えられたんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:30.83,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049794,1050837}What?!{NOTE:へ？！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:32.29,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050837,1052296}Ōsaki-san!{NOTE:おおさきさん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:36.88,Default,Ōsaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053422,1056884}I'm terribly sorry. The melody of that oden stand girl was so straightforward…{NOTE:申し訳ありません。あのおでん屋の娘さんのメロディーが素直で…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:39.09,Default,Ōsaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056884,1059095}It was so simple and raw, it moved my heart.{NOTE:飾り気がなく、それで人の心…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:42.80,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059095,1062807}You idiot! What were you thinking?{NOTE:馬鹿。あなたって言う人は……馬鹿馬鹿！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:46.89,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062807,1066894}Do you realize the position you put my daughter into?{NOTE:あなたは娘の立場をどうしたか分かっていますね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:49.14,Default,Ōsaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066894,1069147}Y-Yes ma'am.{NOTE:あ、は、はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:51.56,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069147,1071566}So what are you going to do now, Ōsaki?{NOTE:どうしてくれるの？おおさき！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:54.11,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071566,1074110}If the school gets wind of it…{NOTE:この事が学校にXX分かれば…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:56.65,Default,Ōsaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074110,1076654}I'll go apologize. To Mine-san, too.{NOTE:はい。お詫び申し上げます。峰さんにも。}
