Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.03,0:18:00.53,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078030,1080533}Your apology doesn't solve anything!{NOTE:お詫びXX問題じゃないのよ、これは！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:04.16,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080533,1084162}Miki, stay calm.{NOTE:みき。冷静に成りなさい。冷静に。}
