Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:11.16,Default,Ōsaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089959,1091169}Oh?{NOTE:お？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:14.54,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092003,1094547}You don't have to apologize.{NOTE:あなたは詫びなんかいれないでいいの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:16.92,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094547,1096924}Just forget the whole thing.{NOTE:このまま忘れてください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:18.17,Default,Ōsaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096924,1098176}Ma'am…{NOTE:奥さん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:21.09,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098176,1101095}Right. That's for the best, Ōsaki.{NOTE:そうね。それがいいわ、おおさき。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:23.13,Default,Ōsaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101095,1103139}Y-Yes ma'am.{NOTE:は、はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:33.85,Default,Kōda Miki's follower B,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110771,1113858}Even though I heard it just once, I won't forget it anytime soon.{NOTE:本当一度聞いただけで忘れられはしないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:36.52,Default,Kōda Miki's follower A,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113858,1116527}Yeah! My heart has melted.{NOTE:そう！ハートはグッと痺れちゃってさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.52,0:18:39.73,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116527,1119739}Well put. Music composition starts inside your heart.{NOTE:そうね。作曲をまず心なのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:43.24,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119739,1123242}Then it's just a matter of finding lyrics that fit the melody.{NOTE:そしてメロディーに歌詞が素直にフィットすること。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:44.36,Default,Unknown student,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123242,1124368}Mine-san.{NOTE:峰さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:45.07,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124368,1125077}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
